LuaScript:
function onLoad()
    setNotes("\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nVerdant: Re-Scripted [ulia]")
    allObjects = getAllObjects()
    refillButton = nil
    for i, o in ipairs(allObjects) do
        if o.hasTag("Refill") then
            refillButton = o
        end
        if o.hasTag("Helper") then
            o.setLock(true)
        end
        if o.hasTag("Locked") then
            o.setLock(true)
            o.interactable = false
        end
    end
    setupUI()
    emptySlots = {}
    refillIndex = 1
end

function setupUI()
    local refillParams = {
        click_function = "refillCards",
        function_owner = Global,
        label          = "re-fill\nstuff",
        position       = {0, 1, 0},
        rotation       = {0, 180, 0},
        width          = 500,
        height         = 500,
        font_size      = 150,
        color          = {1, 1, 1},
        font_color     = {0.2, 0.2, 0.2},
    }
    refillButton.createButton(refillParams)
    refillButton.setColorTint({0,0,0,0})
end

function refillCards()
    local plantDeck = findObjects({-5.00, 2, -1.50})[1].hit_object
    local roomDeck = findObjects({-5.00,  2, -7.50})[1].hit_object
    local itemDeck = findObjects({-5.00,  2, -4.50})[1].hit_object
    plantSnaps = {
        {-3.00, 3, -1.50},
        {-0.99, 3, -1.50},
        {1.00,  3, -1.50},
        {3.00,  3, -1.50}
    }
    itemSnaps = {
        {-3.00, 3, -4.50},
        {-1.00, 3, -4.50},
        {1.00,  3, -4.50},
        {3.00,  3, -4.50}
    }
    roomSnaps = {
        {-3.00, 3, -7.50},
        {-1.00, 3, -7.50},
        {1.00,  3, -7.50},
        {3.00,  3, -7.50}
    }
    emptySlots = {}
    for i, s in ipairs(plantSnaps) do
        if findObjects(s)[1].hit_object.hasTag("Cardplate") then
            local empty = {deck = plantDeck, pos = s}
            table.insert(emptySlots, empty)
        end
    end
    for i, s in ipairs(itemSnaps) do
        if findObjects(s)[1].hit_object.hasTag("Cardplate") then
            local empty = {deck = itemDeck, pos = s}
            table.insert(emptySlots, empty)
        end
    end
    for i, s in ipairs(roomSnaps) do
        if findObjects(s)[1].hit_object.hasTag("Cardplate") then
            local empty = {deck = roomDeck, pos = s}
            table.insert(emptySlots, empty)
        end
    end
    refillIndex = 1
    if #emptySlots > 1 then
        plantDeck.randomize()
        roomDeck.randomize()
        itemDeck.randomize()
        Wait.time(function() placeCards() end, 0.1, #emptySlots)
    end
end

function placeCards()
    local params = {position=emptySlots[refillIndex].pos, flip = true}
    emptySlots[refillIndex].deck.takeObject(params)
    refillIndex = refillIndex + 1
end

function findObjects(pos)
    local hitList = Physics.cast({
        origin       = pos,
        direction    = {0,-1,0},
        type         = 3,
        size         = {0.1,0.1,0.1},
        max_distance = 100,
        debug        = false,
    })
    return hitList
end
